{"tid":1649152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"改革連登","createTime":"2019-10-12T14:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T03:57:10.000Z","uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"561c172e6c72a74b5cca2a732c73582e515579da","tid":1649152,"uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:00:46.000Z","msg":"成也連登，敗也連登<br />\n而家個情況就好似5年前雨傘高登咁<br />\n5毛當道，分化、失敗主義充斥<br />\n<br />\n不過我相信連登係會進化<br />\n之前p牌制度已經杜絕咗一班5毛<br />\n<br />\n但係眼見當下情況又再惡化<br />\n強烈建議連仔幫手<br />\n<br />\n1. Ban中國ip(包括申請帳號、留言，甚至瀏覽)<br />\n<br />\n我相信呢一刻勇武同和理非主力都係位於香港<br />\nBan中國ip就算唔可以限制5毛<br />\n都可以增加大陸維穩成本<br />\n<br />\n2. 強制一次性登出<br />\n<br />\n雖然冇可能證實係咪有黑警用咗被補者帳號/會員賣帳號比5毛<br />\n不過強制登出起碼可以防止呢件事<br />\n我相信冇真連登仔會介意登入一次<br />\n<br />\n其他建議開放討論"},{"pid":"a318ed09cde4ebe89d8961f81bb841ac46fca006","tid":1649152,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"098467562f029fdf006523aee6045fcaa07e5609","tid":1649152,"uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"1. Ban 中國IP<br />\n2. 一次性強制登出"},{"pid":"5b43d42208301cb6c68c2fdc45bd7a00b4d34ce5","tid":1649152,"uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"1. Ban 中國IP<br />\n2. 一次性強制登出"},{"pid":"cb19ed574f5ead42c463ee13125283d095204d6c","tid":1649152,"uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:58:37.000Z","msg":"1. Ban 中國IP<br />\n2. 一次性強制登出"},{"pid":"81c79f95097d027a5eb143990ee62538e520994b","tid":1649152,"uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"1. Ban 中國IP<br />\n2. 一次性強制登出"},{"pid":"eb40df8377ecfcb2fd6f7e9b6f9eb83dfd057d89","tid":1649152,"uid":307389,"like":0,"di